 campus websites, but will need the active cooperation and efforts of campus webmasters for accessibility to be implemented at UIC.        Resource and Site Checks   The Digital Accessibility Committee is available to support campus webmasters. For more information and help with checking a site for accessibility, contact the committee .       Digital Accessibility Commitee Members   George M. Blackwell IT Technical Associate Office of Student Systems Services  Edward Campbell Assistant Director, Creative Services ACCC  Jessica Eisenbeis Assistant Program Director for Online Programs UIC Extended Campus Administration  Debra Hale Associate Director Office of Digital Communications  Raymond Matthes Director of Engineering Media Services College of Engineering  Michael Michela Instructional Development Specialist College of Business Administration – Deans Office  Kavita Mundle Clinical Associate Professor & Electronic Resources Librarian University Library  Daniel Paz-Horta IT Technical Associate – Web Developer Academic and Enrollment Services Information Technology Office of the Vice Provost for Academic and Enrollment Services  Kurt Okimoto Web Specialist Office of Public and Government Affairs  Scott Rozman Information Technology Manager / Administrative Coordinator Administration, LAS          Contact Us    Back to main content           About the Digital Accessibility Committee                  UIC Logo        Digital Accessibility Committee       Contact   Phone: (312) 413-0886  dag@listserv.uic.edu        Social Media Accounts            UIC.edu links   UIC.edu  Academic Calendar  Athletics  Campus Directory  Disability Resources  Emergency Information  Event Calendar  Job Openings  Library  Maps  UIC Safe Mobile App  UIC Today  UI Health  Veterans Affairs        Powered by Red 2.38.0  © 2020 The Board of Trustees of the University of Illinois |  Privacy Statement    Campuses   University of Illinois System  Urbana-Champaign  Springfield      Cookie Settings                 